improved_metadata.title: Spray Foam Warmth
improved_metadata.description: This song is a quirky ode to the insulating power of spray foam. It humorously highlights how spray foam keeps you warm and cozy during cold weather.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Spray foam keeps you warm, keeps you cozy in the storm
